      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is the number one mistake intermediate Scrabble players make?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "The number one mistake is wasting the S tile for fewer than 8 extra points. The S tile has a hook value of 8-10 points because it can pluralize almost any noun or verb on the board, so spending it for a marginal gain destroys future scoring potential." } },
